WEBVTT

00:07:57.704 --> 00:08:00.806
which they can deliver on a bench?

00:08:01.283 --> 00:08:04.180
Empower them with the skills to listen,

00:08:04.966 --> 00:08:06.278
to show empathy,

00:08:07.154 --> 00:08:10.514
all of that rooted
in cognitive behavioral therapy;

00:08:10.538 --> 00:08:15.020
empower them with the skills
to provide behavior activation,

00:08:15.044 --> 00:08:16.876
activity scheduling;

00:08:16.900 --> 00:08:21.473
and support them using digital technology.

00:08:21.497 --> 00:08:23.590
You know, mobile phone technology.

00:08:23.614 --> 00:08:26.246
Pretty much everyone in Africa
has a mobile phone today.

00:08:26.872 --> 00:08:28.637
So in 2006,

00:08:28.661 --> 00:08:30.841
I started my first group